\c 22
\s Umuzi wegazi
\p
\v 1 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* laselifika kimi lisithi:
\v 2 Wena-ke, ndodana yomuntu, uzakwehlulela yini\x + 20.4.\x*, wahlulele umuzi wegazi\x + 23.37.\x*? Yebo uzawazisa zonke izinengiso zawo\x + 16.2.\x*.
\v 3 Ubususithi: Itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Umuzi ochitha igazi phakathi kwawo\x + 22.4,6,9,12,13,27. 7.23. 16.38. 33.25. 36.18. 2 Kho. 21.16.\x*, ukuze isikhathi sawo sifike\x + 21.25,29.\x*, wenze izithombe ezimelene lawo, ukuze uzingcolise\x + 44.25. Levi 15.32. 18.20,23. 19.31. 22.8.\x*.
\v 4 Wena usulecala\x + Zaga 30.10.\x* ngegazi olichithileyo\x + 7.23. 16.38. 22.4,6,9,12,13,27. 33.25. 36.18. 2 Kho. 21.16.\x*, wazingcolisa ngezithombe zakho ozenzileyo, wasondeza insuku zakho\x + 21.25,29.\x*, usufikile eminyakeni yakho\x + Josh. 23.1.\x*. Ngalokho ngikwenzile \add waba li\add*hlazo ezizweni\x + 5.14. 21.28. 23.32. Dan. 9.16.\x* lenhlekisa kuwo wonke amazwe\x + Jer. 20.8.\x*.
\v 5 Abaseduze labakhatshana lawe bazakuhleka usulu, wena ongcolileyo ngebizo, ogcwele isiphithiphithi.
\v 6 Khangela, iziphathamandla zakoIsrayeli zaziphakathi kwakho\x + 22.27.\x*, yileso laleso ngengalo yaso\x + 17.9. Hlab. 79.11.\x*, ukuthi sichithe igazi\x + 7.23. 16.38. 22.4,6,9,12,13,27 .33.25. 36.18. 2 Kho. 21.16.\x*.
\v 7 Baphathe uyihlo lonyoko ngokweyisa kuwe\x + Dute. 27.16. Efe. 6.2.\x*; benze ngocindezelo kowemzini\x + 22.12.\x* phakathi kwakho\x + Eks. 22.21.\x*; bacindezele izintandane lomfelokazi kuwe\x + Eks. 22.22. Jobe 22.9.\x*\x + Levi 19.33.\x*.
\v 8 Uzidelele izinto zami ezingcwele\x + 22.26.\x*, wangcolisa amasabatha ami\x + 20.13,16,21,24. 23.38.\x*.
\v 9 Abantu abahlebayo\x + Levi 19.16. Jer. 6.28. 1 Sam. 22.9.\x* babekuwe ukuze bachithe igazi\x + 7.23. 16.38. 22.4,6,9,12,13,27. 33.25. 36.18. 2 Kho. 21.16.\x*; badla kuwe phezu kwezintaba\x + 18.6.\x*; benza amanyala phakathi kwakho\x + 16.43.\x*.
\v 10 Bembule ubunqunu baboyise phakathi kwakho\x + Levi 18.7,8. 20.11. 1 Kor. 5.1.\x*; bathobise kuwe owesifazana\x + 36.17. Levi 18.19.\x* ongcoliswe yikuba semfuleni\x + 22.10.\x*.
\v 11 Futhi omunye wenze amanyala lomfazi kamakhelwane wakhe\x + 18.11. 33.26. Jer. 5.8. Eks. 20.14.\x*, lomunye wangcolisa umalokazana wakhe ngokuhlazisayo\x + Levi 18.15. 20.12.\x*, lomunye uthobise udadewabo phakathi kwakho, indodakazi kayise\x + Levi 18.9. 20.17.\x*.
\v 12 Phakathi kwakho bemukele izipho\x + Dute. 27.25.\x* ukuze bachithe igazi\x + 22.3.\x*; uyemukela inzalo lokwengezelelweyo\x + 18.8.\x*, uphangile umakhelwane wakho ngocindezelo\x + 22.7.\x*, wangikhohlwa, itsho iNkosi uJehova\x + 23.35. Jer. 2.32.\x*.
