\v 13 Khangela-ke ngitshayile isandla sami\x + 21.14.\x* ngenzuzo yakho embi oyenzileyo\x + 22.27. Jer. 51.13. Jer. 22.17.\x*, langegazi lakho ebeliphakathi kwakho\x + 22.3.\x*.
\v 14 Inhliziyo yakho izakuma yini, kumbe izandla zakho ziqine, ensukwini engizaphathana lawe\x + 21.7. Tshu. 6.10.\x* kizo? Mina N\nd kosi\nd* ngikhulumile, njalo ngizakwenza\x + 17.24.\x*.
\v 15 Ngikuhlakaze phakathi kwezizwe\x + 12.15. 36.19.\x*\x + Dute. 4.27.\x*, ngikusabalalise phakathi kwamazwe\x + 12.15. 36.19.\x*\x + 5.10.\x*, ngiqede ukungcola kwakho kuwe\x + 24.11. 16.41.\x*.
\v 16 Njalo uzangcoliswa phakathi kwakho emehlweni abezizwe\x + 7.24.\x*; ubususazi ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\x + 6.7.\x*\nd*.
