\v 17 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* laselifika kimi lisithi:
\v 18 Ndodana yomuntu, indlu kaIsrayeli isibengamanyele kimi\x + Hlab. 119.119. Zaga 25.4. 26.23. Isa. 1.22,25.\x*; bonke balithusi\x + Jer. 6.28.\x*, lezenge\x + Isa. 1.25.\x*, lensimbi\x + Jer. 6.28.\x*, lomnuso, phakathi kwesithando\x + 22.20,22. Isa. 48.10.\x*; bangamanyele esiliva\x + Jer. 6.30. Mal. 3.3.\x*.
\v 19 Ngakho itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Ngoba lonke selibengamanyele\x + Hlab. 119.119. Zaga 25.4. 26.23. Isa. 1.22,25.\x*, ngakho khangelani, ngizalibuthelela phakathi kweJerusalema.
\v 20 \add Njengoba\add* bebuthelela isiliva lethusi\x + Jer. 6.28.\x* lensimbi lomnuso\x + Jer. 6.28.\x* lezenge\x + Isa. 1.25.\x* phakathi kwesithando\x + 22.20,22. Isa. 48.10.\x*, ukuze bafuthe umlilo phezu kwakho uku\add ku\add*ncibilikisa\x + 21.31.\x*; ngokunjalo ngiza\add li\add*buthelela ekuthukutheleni kwami lelakeni lwami, ngi\add li\add*tshiye, ngilincibilikise\x + Jer. 33.5.\x*.
\v 21 Yebo, ngizalibuthelela, ngivuthele phezu kwenu\x + 21.31.\x* emlilweni wentukuthelo yami, beselincibilikiswa phakathi kwawo\x + 22.31.\x*.
\v 22 Njengesiliva sincibilikiswa phakathi kwesithando, ngokunjalo lizancibilikiswa phakathi kwaso\x + 22.20,22. Isa. 48.10.\x*; njalo lizakwazi ukuthi mina N\nd kosi\nd* ngithulule ulaka lwami phezu kwenu\x + 7.8. 22.31.\x*.
