\v 23 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* laselifika kimi lisithi:
\v 24 Ndodana yomuntu, wothi kiyo: Wena uyilizwe elingahlanjululwanga, \add le\add*linganethwanga ngosuku lwentukuthelo\x + 34.26. Hlab. 68.9. 1 Kho. 8.36. Levi 26.4.\x*.
\v 25 Ugobe lwabaprofethi bayo phakathi kwayo\x + Hos. 6.9. Jer. 11.9.\x* lunjengesilwane esibhongayo\x + 19.3. Zef. 3.3.\x* esidlithiza impango\x + 22.27. 19.3,6.\x*; bayidlile imiphefumulo\x + Mat. 23.14.\x*, bathatha\x + Mika 3.11.\x* inotho\x + Zaga 27.24.\x* lezinto eziligugu\x + Jer. 20.5.\x*, benza abafelokazi baba banengi phakathi kwayo.
\v 26 Abapristi bayo\x + Mal. 2.8. Lilo 4.13.\x* baphathe umlayo wami ngodlakela\x + Zef. 3.4.\x*, bangcolisa izinto zami ezingcwele\x + Zef. 3.4.\x*\x + 22.16. 28.18.\x*; kabenzanga mehluko phakathi kokungcwele lokungcolileyo\x + 42.20. 44.23. Levi 10.10.\x*; kabazisanga\x + 42.20. 44.23. Levi 10.10.\x* \add umehluko\add* phakathi kokungcolileyo lokuhlambulukileyo\x + 22.2.\x*; bafihla amehlo abo kumasabatha ami\x + 44.24. Neh. 13.15. Jer. 17.22,24,27.\x*; ngakho ngangcoliswa phakathi kwabo\x + 22.16. 28.18.\x*.
\v 27 Iziphathamandla zayo phakathi kwayo\x + 22.3,6. Isa. 1.23. Mika 3.1,2,3,9,10,11.\x* zinjengezimpisi\x + Zef. 3.3. Gen. 49.27. Mat. 7.15.\x* ezidlithiza impango\x + 22.27. 19.3,6.\x*, ukuthi zichithe igazi\x + 22.3,6. Isa. 1.23. Mika 3.1,2,3,9,10,11.\x*, zibhubhise imiphefumulo, ukuze zizuze inzuzo embi\x + 22.3,6. Isa. 1.23. Mika 3.1,2,3,9,10,11.\x*\x + 22.13.\x*.
\v 28 Labaprofethi bayo babacombe ngekalaga\x + 13.10.\x*, bebona okuyize\x + 13.6.\x*, bebavumisa amanga, besithi: Itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova; kanti iN\nd kosi\nd* ingakhulumanga\x + 13.6.\x*.
\v 29 Abantu belizwe bacindezele \add ng\add*ocindezelo, baphanga impango\x + 18.12.\x*, bacindezela umyanga loswelayo\x + 18.12.\x*, bacindezela owezizwe kungelakulunga\x + 22.7.\x*.
\v 30 Njalo ngadinga umuntu phakathi kwabo\x + Jer. 5.1. Isa. 59.16.\x* ongabiya uthango\x + 13.5.\x*\x + Isa. 58.12.\x*, ame esikhexeni phambi kwami emele ilizwe ukuze ngingalichithi, kodwa kangi\add m\add*tholanga\x + 13.5.\x*.
\v 31 Ngakho ngithululele intukuthelo yami phezu kwabo\x + 22.22.\x*, ngibaqede ngomlilo wolaka lwami\x + 22.21.\x*; ngehlisele indlela yabo phezu kwekhanda labo, itsho iNkosi uJehova\x + 7.4.\x*.
